data.description: DRASTIC PRICE REDUCTION! Seller is motivated and ready to close. This beautiful home built in 2017 with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms is only 2 miles from Rockmart and US-278. Sitting on .48 acres with close proximity to shopping and dining, makes this home perfect. Inside, is a welcoming foyer, an amazing kitchen has stained cabinets, granite countertops, an island, walk-in panty, and a built-in desk area. Separating the kitchen and living room is a granite bar with a view to the fireplace. The covered back patio with a ceiling fan and the large level back yard adds an additional space for all to enjoy. Upstairs, there is a loft area, laundry, and 4 bedrooms including the owners suite that is a must see. A nice sitting area, huge walk in closet, double vanities, and a soaking tub are a few of the features in the primary suite. Schedule a tour today to see all that this home has to offer.
